Interface DeckOfCardsManagerListener

public interface DeckOfCardsManagerListener

Listener for the Toq app's API service lifecycle and applet installation events.

Author:
mcaunter

Method Summary
 void onConnected()
          Called upon establishing a connection with the Toq app's API service.
 void onDisconnected()
          Called upon disconnecting from the Toq app's API service.
 void onInstallationDenied()
          Called if the user has denied the deck of cards applet installation request.
 void onInstallationSuccessful()
          Called if the user has approved the deck of cards applet installation and the installation process has completed successfully.
 void onUninstalled()
          Called upon the uninstall of the deck of cards applet.
